            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " feels like the video game equivalent of the opening act for an indie rock show: while they do have potential, you are really there to listen to the headline act and find yourself waiting for them to finish their set.",
